Answer for Exercise 5 -

Program â€“
sandwich_orders = ['pastrami', 'potato','grilled cheese','omelette','paneer','pastrami','veggie', 'chicken tandoori', 'chicken tikka','pastrami']
finished_sandwiches = []

print("I'm sorry, we're all out of pastrami today.")
while 'pastrami' in sandwich_orders:
    sandwich_orders.remove('pastrami')

print("\n")
while sandwich_orders:
    current_sandwich = sandwich_orders.pop()
    print(f"I'm working on your {current_sandwich} sandwich.")
    finished_sandwiches.append(current_sandwich)

print("\n")
for sandwich in finished_sandwiches:
    print(f"I made a {sandwich} sandwich.")
    
Output - 
I'm sorry, we're all out of pastrami today.

I'm working on your chicken tikka sandwich.
I'm working on your chicken tandoori sandwich.
I'm working on your veggie sandwich.
I'm working on your paneer sandwich.
I'm working on your omelette sandwich.
I'm working on your grilled cheese sandwich.
I'm working on your potato sandwich.

I made a chicken tikka sandwich.
I made a chicken tandoori sandwich.
I made a veggie sandwich.
I made a paneer sandwich.
I made a omelette sandwich.
I made a grilled cheese sandwich.
I made a potato sandwich.
